---

# Master Responsibilities

This is the most important component.

```text
Receive Commands

↓

Resolve Zone

↓

Connect Slave

↓

Modbus TCP

↓

Execute Command

↓

Collect Response

↓

Return Status

↓

Send Heartbeat
```

The Master is your **gateway**.

---

# Slave Responsibilities

Each slave should only do one job.

```text
Start Modbus TCP Server

↓

Wait For Request

↓

Receive Coil Command

↓

Switch Relay

↓

Return Response
```

Nothing else.

No database.

No schedules.

No business logic.

